{"tid":106251,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇養魚(金魚)嘅巴打","createTime":"2017-02-03T13:30:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-16T07:56:02.000Z","uid":55514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e9e47e781d37f75b08fff7a3340853c9ac7281af","tid":106251,"uid":55514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T13:30:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/03/212910_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F03%2F212910_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=15c9c6f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/03/212916_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F03%2F212916_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=082baff7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屋企啲魚唔知咩事，生啲白色野之後就會死<br />\n老豆已經換左過濾<br />\n又滴過藥水<br />\n水都大換左幾次<br />\n已經死左2輪魚<br />\n依轉第3輪<br />\n已經養左十幾年魚<br />\n老豆都好無奈好心痛"},{"pid":"13bfd8d60b59e1f7a32ef1741d460a70f60502e4","tid":106251,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T17:20:01.000Z","msg":"衣家先睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有冇養魚？"},{"pid":"558c375a71afc6c54a2319ec4323644244966797","tid":106251,"uid":55514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T03:04:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>衣家先睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有冇養魚？</blockquote><br />\n有，依家得番三條金魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13f3dd13a64cabd9d0a15419cbde658714149a7e","tid":106251,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T07:28:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>衣家先睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有冇養魚？</blockquote><br />\n有，依家得番三條金魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇全缸圖睇下<br />\n同埋過濾器入面擺左乜野擺左幾多"},{"pid":"3e29674f3a8307741ec74dfa3f6df3bddb542d48","tid":106251,"uid":55514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T07:56:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>衣家先睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有冇養魚？</blockquote><br />\n有，依家得番三條金魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇全缸圖睇下<br />\n同埋過濾器入面擺左乜野擺左幾多</blockquote><br />\n過兩日"}]}